title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – May 18 2022

description:
C&B's PA primary show -- with live interviews with three GOP candidates -- produces photo finish between Dr. Oz and Dave McCormick. Soviet Mary Poppins resigns. Covid cases and hospitalizations explode nationwide. Bridge Colby, formerly of the Trump Pentagon, joins Clay and Buck to talk about the war in Ukraine. Fauci says he doesn't like mandating things. C&B take calls.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
